OL,5,G0240 Father Brown
OL,6,     FAfter an heiress makes her will
OL,7,     Fout to the leader of a bogus
OL,8,     Freligious cult and mysteriously
OL,9,     Ffalls to her death, Brown finds
OL,10,     Fthat he is the charlatan's alibi.
OL,11,G0335 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,12,     FGeorge asks important questions
OL,13,     Flike 'Can news broadcasting be
OL,14,     Ftruly unbiased?', 'Is it right to
OL,15,     Fignore Government pressure?', and
OL,16,     F'Where the hell are my ulcer
OL,17,     Fpills?'
